ABOUT ME

Expert NLP & Agents

for Health Tech.

As a remote freelance Senior Data Scientist, I partner with innovative companies in the wellness, longevity, and biohacking sectors. I bring a blend of deep technical skill in NLP/ML and AI Agent development, creative problem-solving (proven by Kaggle Silver & Bronze medals), and full-cycle development experience (including 5 years as a full-stack developer) to deliver impactful, end-to-end AI solutions.

I specialize in applying cutting-edge AI: particularly LLMs and agent-based systems, to validate concepts, unlock funding opportunities, and build unique capabilities for my clients. Whether it's developing knowledge extraction pipelines from research/media, creating custom AI agents (integrating with tools like FlowiseAI/n8n), or designing novel NLP models, I deliver robust, creative AI solutions tailored to the specific challenges within the wellness and research space.
